<i>adjective</i>: 참담하다 [참담하다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>참담하다 [참담하다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. disastrous; terrible</dd><br>
<dd>끔찍하고 절망적이다.</dd><br>
<dd>Horrible and hopeless.</dd><br>
<dd>2. miserable</dd><br>
<dd>몹시 슬프고 괴롭다.</dd><br>
<dd>Very sad and painful.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>